<Routes>
  <Route
    path="/"
    element={
      !showQuizPage ? (
        quizData.map((data, index) => (
          <QuizCard
            key={data.uuid}
            startQuiz={() => startQuiz(data.mode)}
            mode={data.mode}
            uuid={data.uuid}
            category={data.categories[0]}
          />
        ))
      ) : null
    }
  />
</Routes>
